PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FIran and the United States say
OL,8,Fprogress is being made in peace talks,
OL,9,Fbut the Strait of Hormuz remains
OL,10,Fclosed, with oil tankers once again
OL,11,Ftrapped near the shipping lane.
OL,13,FIt comes after Iran reversed its
OL,14,Fdecision to reopen the vital
OL,15,Fthoroughfare on Saturday, April 18,
OL,16,Fand warned that it would continue to
OL,17,Fblock transit through the strait as
OL,18,Flong as the US blockade of Iranian
OL,19,Fports remained in effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FOn Friday, April 17, Iran had said
OL,8,Fvessels could move through the strait
OL,9,Fin coordination with it and against
OL,10,Fthe payment of a toll.
OL,12,FHowever, in a statement on Saturday
OL,13,Fevening, carried by Iran's state
OL,14,Fmedia, the navy warned that any
OL,15,Fviolating vessel would be targeted.
OL,17,FIran considers the US blockade a
OL,18,Fviolation of the ceasefire between the
OL,19,Ftwo countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FIran negotiator says strait will
OL,8,Fremain closed
OL,10,FIran's parliamentary Speaker Mohammed
OL,11,FBagher Qalibaf says the Strait of
OL,12,FHormuz will remain closed as long as
OL,13,Fthe US imposes a naval blockade on
OL,14,FIran.
OL,16,F"It is impossible for others to pass
OL,17,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz while we
OL,18,Fcannot," he said in televised comments
OL,19,Faired by Iranian media on Saturday
OL,20,Fevening.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FQalibaf, who is Iran's chief
OL,8,Fnegotiator with the United States,
OL,9,Fsaid that the strait is now under
OL,10,FIran's control, linking the reopening
OL,11,Fto the US lifting of its blockade.
OL,13,F"If the US does not lift the blockade,
OL,14,Ftraffic in the Strait of Hormuz will
OL,15,Fdefinitely be restricted," he said.
OL,17,FHe said that the ceasefire was on
OL,18,Fverge of collapse when the US
OL,19,Fattempted to mine-clear the strait. He
OL,20,Fsaid Iran viewed the US attempt as a
OL,21,Fviolation of the ceasefire.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"The situation escalated to the point
OL,8,Fof conflict but the enemy retreated,"
OL,9,Fhe said.
OL,11,FThe escalating standoff over the
OL,12,Fcritical route threatens to deepen the
OL,13,Fenergy crisis roiling the global
OL,14,Feconomy and push the two countries
OL,15,Ftoward renewed conflict.
OL,17,FAccording to the United Kingdom
OL,18,FMaritime Trade Operations Centre,
OL,19,Fhours earlier, two gunboats from
OL,20,FIran's Revolutionary Guard opened fire
OL,21,Fon a tanker transiting the strait.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FIt reported the tanker and crew as
OL,8,Fsafe, without identifying the vessel
OL,9,For its destination.
OL,11,FTwo Indian-flagged ships were also
OL,12,Finvolved in a "shooting incident" in
OL,13,Fthe Strait earlier Saturday, India's
OL,14,Fforeign ministry said.
OL,16,FRoughly one-fifth of the world's oil
OL,17,Fpasses through the strait and further
OL,18,Flimits would squeeze already
OL,19,Fconstrained supply, driving prices
OL,20,Fhigher once again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FIran's announcement about the opening
OL,8,Fof the crucial body of water came as a
OL,9,F10-day truce between Israel and the
OL,10,FIranian-backed Hezbollah militant
OL,11,Fgroup in Lebanon appeared to hold.
OL,13,FThe fighting has killed at least 3,000
OL,14,Fpeople in Iran, nearly 2,300 in
OL,15,FLebanon, 23 in Israel and more than a
OL,16,Fdozen in Gulf Arab states. Thirteen US
OL,17,Fservice members have also died.
OL,19,FIran's deputy foreign minister warns
OL,20,Fagainst US "maximalist" demands
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FIran is not yet ready to hold a new
OL,8,Fround of face-to-face talks with the
OL,9,FUS, due to Washington's "maximalist"
OL,10,Fdemands, a senior Iranian official
OL,11,Fsaid on Saturday.
OL,13,FIranian Deputy Foreign Minister Saeed
OL,14,FKhatibzadeh told Associated Press that
OL,15,Falthough there had been messages
OL,16,Fexchanged between his country and the
OL,17,FUnited States, no meeting was yet
OL,18,Forganised, even as the countries reach
OL,19,Fthe expiry of their two-week ceasefire
OL,20,Fon April 22.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"We are still not there yet to move on
OL,8,Fto an actual meeting because there are
OL,9,Fissues that the Americans have not yet
OL,10,Fabandoned their maximalist position,"
OL,11,FKhatibzadeh said.
OL,13,FIran was seeking the finalisation of a
OL,14,F"framework agreement" before moving to
OL,15,Fan in-person meeting, he added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@eO]vD@AOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
