OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FThe Iranian official would not go into
OL,8,Fspecifics of the negotiations with the
OL,9,FUnited States or say which issues
OL,10,Fremain unresolved but called on
OL,11,FWashington to address Iran's concerns,
OL,12,Fincluding sanctions imposed on Iran.
OL,14,FTrump warns Iran against
OL,15,F"blackmailing" US
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
