CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FMeanwhile, US President Donald Trump
OL,8,Fhas said there are "very good
OL,9,Fconversations going on" between the US
OL,10,Fand Iran, but warned them against
OL,11,F"blackmailing us", adding, "they got a
OL,12,Flittle cute."
OL,14,FAs recently as Friday, Iranian foreign
OL,15,Fminister Abbas Araghchi said that in
OL,16,Fline with a ceasefire agreement
OL,17,Fbetween Israel and Lebanon, the Strait
OL,18,Fof Hormuz was "completely open" for
OL,19,Fall commercial vessels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FSpeaking at an event that evening,
OL,8,FTrump said said that while the strait
OL,9,Fwas "fully open and ready for full
OL,10,Fpassage", the US would "have to finish
OL,11,Fthe deal before we open it for Iran".
OL,13,FThis appeared to present a red line
OL,14,Ffor Tehran, with top Iranian officials
OL,15,Fclaiming the US blockade violated a
OL,16,Ffragile ceasefire agreement between
OL,17,Fthe two countries.
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@HO]rD@XOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FEarly on Saturday, Iran's
OL,8,Fparliamentary speaker Mohammad Bagher
OL,9,FQalibaf posted on X that if the US
OL,10,Fblockade continued "the Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz will not remain open".
OL,13,FAsked by a reporter on Friday night
OL,14,Fwhat he will do if there's no deal
OL,15,Fwhen a ceasefire with Iran expires
OL,16,Fnext week, Trump said: "I don't know.
OL,17,FMaybe I won't extend it, but the
OL,18,Fblockade is going to remain.
OL,26,@rD@TOUsD@\O]xD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"But maybe I won't extend it, so
OL,8,Fyou'll have a blockade and
OL,9,Funfortunately we'll have to start
OL,10,Fdropping bombs again."
OL,12,FHowever, Trump also told reporters
OL,13,Faccompanying him aboard Air Force One
OL,14,Fto Washington that, "I think it's
OL,15,Fgoing to happen," referring to a deal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@VO]vD@UOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FDespite the escalation in the Strait
OL,8,Fof Hormuz, officials in Pakistan, who
OL,9,Fhelped broker the current truce, say
OL,10,Fthe United States and Iran are still
OL,11,Fmoving closer to a deal ahead of the
OL,12,FApril 22 ceasefire deadline.
OL,14,FSpeaking at a diplomatic forum in
OL,15,FAntalya, Turkey, Pakistan's Foreign
OL,16,FMinister Ishaq Dar said the separate
OL,17,Fceasefire in Lebanon was a positive
OL,18,Fsign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FHe noted that fighting between Israel
OL,8,Fand Hezbollah had been a key sticking
OL,9,Fpoint before talks in Islamabad ended
OL,10,F"very close" to an agreement last
OL,11,Fweekend.
OL,13,FPakistan is expected to host a second
OL,14,Fround of talks between Iran and the US
OL,15,Fearly next week.
OL,17,FQuestions remain over Lebanon truce
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
