OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FThe US and Iran are in the middle of a
OL,8,Ffragile truce which is due to last
OL,9,Funtil April 22, while Israel and
OL,10,FLebanon have begun a 10-day ceasefire.
OL,12,FWhile mediators have been optimistic,
OL,13,Fit is unclear to what extent Hezbollah
OL,14,Fwill abide by the truce between the
OL,15,FLebanese and Israeli governments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FThe militant group did not play a role
OL,8,Fin ceasefire talks and has previously
OL,9,Fsaid it would not recognise the
OL,10,Flegitimacy of the negotiations, which
OL,11,Fhave allowed Israel to continue
OL,12,Foccupying a stretch of southern
OL,13,FLebanon.
OL,15,FTrump said in another post that Israel
OL,16,Fis "prohibited" by the US from further
OL,17,Fstrikes on Lebanon and that "enough is
OL,18,Fenough" in the Israel-Hezbollah war.
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@OO]yD@]OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FThe State Department said the
OL,8,Fprohibition applies only to offensive
OL,9,Fattacks and not to actions taken in
OL,10,Fself-defence.
OL,12,FOn Saturday, French President Emmanuel
OL,13,FMacron says a French soldier was
OL,14,Fkilled and three others wounded in an
OL,15,Fattack on UN peacekeepers in southern
OL,16,FLebanon.
OL,18,FBoth Macron and the UNIFIL force
OL,19,Fblamed Hezbollah, but the militant
OL,20,Fgroup denied involvement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776679573
OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FIn a post on X on Saturday night, the
OL,8,FUN's secretary-general Antonio
OL,9,FGuterres condemned the attack and
OL,10,Fcalled on all parties to respect the
OL,11,Fceasefire.
OL,13,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,14,FNetanyahu had said Israel agreed to
OL,15,Fthe ceasefire in Lebanon "at the
OL,16,Frequest of my friend President Trump,"
OL,17,Fbut that the campaign against
OL,18,FHezbollah is not complete.
OL,26,@pD@[rwwD@ZOUxD@fO]
