OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FHe claimed Israel had destroyed about
OL,8,F90% of Hezbollah's missile and rocket
OL,9,Fstockpiles and added that Israeli
OL,10,Fforces "have not finished yet" with
OL,11,Fthe dismantling of the group.
OL,13,FIn Beirut, displaced families began
OL,14,Fmoving toward southern Lebanon and
OL,15,FBeirut's southern suburbs despite
OL,16,Fwarnings by officials not to return to
OL,17,Ftheir homes until it became clear
OL,18,Fwhether the ceasefire would hold.
