OL,3,CIran doubles down on closing the
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz as ceasefire deadline
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FThe Lebanese army and UN peacekeepers
OL,8,Fin southern Lebanon reported sporadic
OL,9,Fartillery shelling in some parts of
OL,10,Fsouthern Lebanon in the hours after
OL,11,Fthe ceasefire took effect.
OL,13,FThe war, which began with US and
OL,14,FIsraeli strikes on February 28 has
OL,15,Fkilled at least 3,000 people in Iran,
OL,16,Fmore than 2,290 in Lebanon, 23 in
OL,17,FIsrael and more than a dozen in Gulf
OL,18,FArab states. Meanwhile 13 US service
OL,19,Fmembers have been killed.
